{"componentChunkName":"component---node-modules-gatsby-theme-portfolio-minimal-src-templates-article-index-tsx","path":"/my-first-article/redis/redis5/","result":{"pageContext":{"article":{"banner":{"alt":"Redis","caption":"Photo by <u><a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/Nc5Q_CEcY44\">Redis</a></u>","src":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/062c55607957fedfbebd3eaaab55825c/ca4aa/redis_img.png","srcSet":"/static/062c55607957fedfbebd3eaaab55825c/77001/redis_img.png 75w,\n/static/062c55607957fedfbebd3eaaab55825c/4ec1c/redis_img.png 150w,\n/static/062c55607957fedfbebd3eaaab55825c/ca4aa/redis_img.png 300w","sizes":"(min-width: 300px) 300px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/062c55607957fedfbebd3eaaab55825c/dd377/redis_img.webp 75w,\n/static/062c55607957fedfbebd3eaaab55825c/40ac4/redis_img.webp 150w,\n/static/062c55607957fedfbebd3eaaab55825c/9e761/redis_img.webp 300w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 300px) 300px, 100vw"}]},"width":660,"height":400.40000000000003}}}},"body":"<h2>HttpSession이란??</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>HttpSession은 Java의 인터페이스(interface)이며, 이를 사용하여 세션(session)을 제어할 수 있습니다. session은 쿠키(cookie)의 트래픽(traffic) 이슈(issue)와 cookie 변경으로 인한 보안 issue를 해결하기 위해 등장했습니다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>라고 구글에 검색을 하면 제일 먼저 나온다. HTTP요청에는 상태가 없으며 각각의 요청이 독립적으로 이뤄지며 서버는 사용자가 보낸 몇번째 요청인지를 저장하지 않는다. 즉, 사용자 브라우저 측에서 자신을 식별할 수 있는 정보를 서버에 요청할때 마다 알려줘야 한다.</p>\n<p>이때 사용자의 브라우저에 응답을 보내면서, 브라우저에 특정 데이터를 저장하도록 전달할 수 있다. 이때 서버에서 작성해서 응답을 받은 브라우저가 저장하는 데이터를 <code class=\"language-text\">쿠키</code>라고 부른다.</p>\n<p>쿠키에 요청을 보낸 브라우저를 특정값을 보내줄 수 있다. 이후 사용자가 요청하면 서버에 저장해놓은 정보로 누구인지 구분할 수 있다. 이런식으로 상태를 저장하지 않는 HTTP 통신을 사용하면서, 이전에 요청을 보낸 사용자를 기억하는 상태를 유지하는 것을 <code class=\"language-text\">세션</code>이라고 부른다.</p>\n<p>SpringBoot를 사용하면, Tomcat 서버가 세션을 생성한다. 그리고 JSESSIONID라는 쿠키 값은 서버 내부의 Tomcat이 처음 접근하는 브라우저에게 발급하는 쿠키이다. Tomcat은 이 쿠키의 값을 바탕으로 세션을 관리하고, HttpSession 객체로 만들어 주고, Spring Boot는 HttpSession을 가져와 사용할 수 있다.</p>\n<h3>실습해보기</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>com.sparata.redis 서버 생성하기</li>\n</ul>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 84.84848484848484%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/1f6300c4ed790128901e5fc3f33048c2/c9b55/2-1-redis-spring.webp 165w,\n/static/1f6300c4ed790128901e5fc3f33048c2/f2908/2-1-redis-spring.webp 330w,\n/static/1f6300c4ed790128901e5fc3f33048c2/cc661/2-1-redis-spring.webp 660w,\n/static/1f6300c4ed790128901e5fc3f33048c2/a66df/2-1-redis-spring.webp 990w,\n/static/1f6300c4ed790128901e5fc3f33048c2/d33d4/2-1-redis-spring.webp 1320w,\n/static/1f6300c4ed790128901e5fc3f33048c2/9a996/2-1-redis-spring.webp 1378w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/1f6300c4ed790128901e5fc3f33048c2/04c57/2-1-redis-spring.png 165w,\n/static/1f6300c4ed790128901e5fc3f33048c2/d9ecf/2-1-redis-spring.png 330w,\n/static/1f6300c4ed790128901e5fc3f33048c2/1f083/2-1-redis-spring.png 660w,\n/static/1f6300c4ed790128901e5fc3f33048c2/7a3d6/2-1-redis-spring.png 990w,\n/static/1f6300c4ed790128901e5fc3f33048c2/78958/2-1-redis-spring.png 1320w,\n/static/1f6300c4ed790128901e5fc3f33048c2/e40ed/2-1-redis-spring.png 1378w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/1f6300c4ed790128901e5fc3f33048c2/1f083/2-1-redis-spring.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"com.sparata.redis\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>com.sparata.redis</p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<ul>\n<li>SessionController.java 파일 생성하기</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">@RestController\npublic class SessionController {\n    @GetMapping(\"/set\")\n    public String set(\n            @RequestParam(\"q\")\n            String q,\n            HttpSession session\n    ) {\n        session.setAttribute(\"q\", q);\n        return \"Saved: \" + q;\n    }\n\n    @GetMapping(\"/get\")\n    public String get(\n            HttpSession session\n    ) {\n        return String.valueOf(session.getAttribute(\"q\"));\n    }\n}</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>test 하기</li>\n</ul>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 87.27272727272728%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/e77b63c80c06c2e54d7ac8e852c0c333/c9b55/2-1-test-1.webp 165w,\n/static/e77b63c80c06c2e54d7ac8e852c0c333/f2908/2-1-test-1.webp 330w,\n/static/e77b63c80c06c2e54d7ac8e852c0c333/cc661/2-1-test-1.webp 660w,\n/static/e77b63c80c06c2e54d7ac8e852c0c333/a66df/2-1-test-1.webp 990w,\n/static/e77b63c80c06c2e54d7ac8e852c0c333/d33d4/2-1-test-1.webp 1320w,\n/static/e77b63c80c06c2e54d7ac8e852c0c333/89344/2-1-test-1.webp 1340w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/e77b63c80c06c2e54d7ac8e852c0c333/04c57/2-1-test-1.png 165w,\n/static/e77b63c80c06c2e54d7ac8e852c0c333/d9ecf/2-1-test-1.png 330w,\n/static/e77b63c80c06c2e54d7ac8e852c0c333/1f083/2-1-test-1.png 660w,\n/static/e77b63c80c06c2e54d7ac8e852c0c333/7a3d6/2-1-test-1.png 990w,\n/static/e77b63c80c06c2e54d7ac8e852c0c333/78958/2-1-test-1.png 1320w,\n/static/e77b63c80c06c2e54d7ac8e852c0c333/acf8f/2-1-test-1.png 1340w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/e77b63c80c06c2e54d7ac8e852c0c333/1f083/2-1-test-1.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"http://localhost:8080/set?q=owen\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p><a href=\"http://localhost:8080/set?q=owen\">http://localhost:8080/set?q=owen</a></p></figcaption>\n  </figure>\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 87.27272727272728%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/bd9796ce8d70eee6f16a11accaf9b9bd/c9b55/2-1-test-2.webp 165w,\n/static/bd9796ce8d70eee6f16a11accaf9b9bd/f2908/2-1-test-2.webp 330w,\n/static/bd9796ce8d70eee6f16a11accaf9b9bd/cc661/2-1-test-2.webp 660w,\n/static/bd9796ce8d70eee6f16a11accaf9b9bd/a66df/2-1-test-2.webp 990w,\n/static/bd9796ce8d70eee6f16a11accaf9b9bd/d33d4/2-1-test-2.webp 1320w,\n/static/bd9796ce8d70eee6f16a11accaf9b9bd/89344/2-1-test-2.webp 1340w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/bd9796ce8d70eee6f16a11accaf9b9bd/04c57/2-1-test-2.png 165w,\n/static/bd9796ce8d70eee6f16a11accaf9b9bd/d9ecf/2-1-test-2.png 330w,\n/static/bd9796ce8d70eee6f16a11accaf9b9bd/1f083/2-1-test-2.png 660w,\n/static/bd9796ce8d70eee6f16a11accaf9b9bd/7a3d6/2-1-test-2.png 990w,\n/static/bd9796ce8d70eee6f16a11accaf9b9bd/78958/2-1-test-2.png 1320w,\n/static/bd9796ce8d70eee6f16a11accaf9b9bd/acf8f/2-1-test-2.png 1340w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/bd9796ce8d70eee6f16a11accaf9b9bd/1f083/2-1-test-2.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"http://localhost:8080/get\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p><a href=\"http://localhost:8080/get\">http://localhost:8080/get</a></p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h3>Scale-Out Test</h3>\n<p>사용자가 급증해서 Scale-Out를 했다. 지금 현재 A서버,B서버가 있다고 하면 사용자가 A 서버로 요청을 했다가, B 서버로 요청을 하게 된다면 세션이 유지될 수 있을까?? 한번 알아보자</p>\n<ul>\n<li>8081 생성하기</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://jiminchur.github.io/my-first-article/sparta3/\">👉🏻 [SpartaCodingClub] JAVA 단기 심화 부트캠프 TIL (3)</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>여기서 자세하게 다루니 추가적으로 적진 않겠다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Redis를 연결하지 않고 우선 test</li>\n</ul>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 87.27272727272728%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/0dd4df639e0be52a079927ef85c19a53/c9b55/2-1-tom-session.webp 165w,\n/static/0dd4df639e0be52a079927ef85c19a53/f2908/2-1-tom-session.webp 330w,\n/static/0dd4df639e0be52a079927ef85c19a53/cc661/2-1-tom-session.webp 660w,\n/static/0dd4df639e0be52a079927ef85c19a53/a66df/2-1-tom-session.webp 990w,\n/static/0dd4df639e0be52a079927ef85c19a53/d33d4/2-1-tom-session.webp 1320w,\n/static/0dd4df639e0be52a079927ef85c19a53/89344/2-1-tom-session.webp 1340w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/0dd4df639e0be52a079927ef85c19a53/04c57/2-1-tom-session.png 165w,\n/static/0dd4df639e0be52a079927ef85c19a53/d9ecf/2-1-tom-session.png 330w,\n/static/0dd4df639e0be52a079927ef85c19a53/1f083/2-1-tom-session.png 660w,\n/static/0dd4df639e0be52a079927ef85c19a53/7a3d6/2-1-tom-session.png 990w,\n/static/0dd4df639e0be52a079927ef85c19a53/78958/2-1-tom-session.png 1320w,\n/static/0dd4df639e0be52a079927ef85c19a53/acf8f/2-1-tom-session.png 1340w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/0dd4df639e0be52a079927ef85c19a53/1f083/2-1-tom-session.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"http://localhost:8080/set?q=tom\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p><a href=\"http://localhost:8080/set?q=tom\">http://localhost:8080/set?q=tom</a></p></figcaption>\n  </figure>\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 87.27272727272728%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/82a5109cee8b6ff535023d232a86c184/c9b55/2-1-tom-get.webp 165w,\n/static/82a5109cee8b6ff535023d232a86c184/f2908/2-1-tom-get.webp 330w,\n/static/82a5109cee8b6ff535023d232a86c184/cc661/2-1-tom-get.webp 660w,\n/static/82a5109cee8b6ff535023d232a86c184/a66df/2-1-tom-get.webp 990w,\n/static/82a5109cee8b6ff535023d232a86c184/d33d4/2-1-tom-get.webp 1320w,\n/static/82a5109cee8b6ff535023d232a86c184/89344/2-1-tom-get.webp 1340w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/82a5109cee8b6ff535023d232a86c184/04c57/2-1-tom-get.png 165w,\n/static/82a5109cee8b6ff535023d232a86c184/d9ecf/2-1-tom-get.png 330w,\n/static/82a5109cee8b6ff535023d232a86c184/1f083/2-1-tom-get.png 660w,\n/static/82a5109cee8b6ff535023d232a86c184/7a3d6/2-1-tom-get.png 990w,\n/static/82a5109cee8b6ff535023d232a86c184/78958/2-1-tom-get.png 1320w,\n/static/82a5109cee8b6ff535023d232a86c184/acf8f/2-1-tom-get.png 1340w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/82a5109cee8b6ff535023d232a86c184/1f083/2-1-tom-get.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"http://localhost:8080/get\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p><a href=\"http://localhost:8080/get\">http://localhost:8080/get</a></p></figcaption>\n  </figure>\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 87.27272727272728%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/19547df019815416d7a63daee0c9fa64/c9b55/2-1-8081-null.webp 165w,\n/static/19547df019815416d7a63daee0c9fa64/f2908/2-1-8081-null.webp 330w,\n/static/19547df019815416d7a63daee0c9fa64/cc661/2-1-8081-null.webp 660w,\n/static/19547df019815416d7a63daee0c9fa64/a66df/2-1-8081-null.webp 990w,\n/static/19547df019815416d7a63daee0c9fa64/d33d4/2-1-8081-null.webp 1320w,\n/static/19547df019815416d7a63daee0c9fa64/89344/2-1-8081-null.webp 1340w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/19547df019815416d7a63daee0c9fa64/04c57/2-1-8081-null.png 165w,\n/static/19547df019815416d7a63daee0c9fa64/d9ecf/2-1-8081-null.png 330w,\n/static/19547df019815416d7a63daee0c9fa64/1f083/2-1-8081-null.png 660w,\n/static/19547df019815416d7a63daee0c9fa64/7a3d6/2-1-8081-null.png 990w,\n/static/19547df019815416d7a63daee0c9fa64/78958/2-1-8081-null.png 1320w,\n/static/19547df019815416d7a63daee0c9fa64/acf8f/2-1-8081-null.png 1340w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/19547df019815416d7a63daee0c9fa64/1f083/2-1-8081-null.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"http://localhost:8081/get\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p><a href=\"http://localhost:8081/get\">http://localhost:8081/get</a></p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>8080포트에서는 정상적으로 작동을 했지만 8081로 오니까 null로 리턴되는 걸 알 수가있다.</p>\n<h2>Sticky Session</h2>\n<p>사용자가 보낸 요청을 하나의 서버로 고정하는 방법이다. 요청을 분산하는 로드밸런서를 통해 요청을 보낸 사용자를 기록, 해당 사용자가 다시 요청을 할 경우 최초로 요청이 전달된 서버로 요청을 전달하는 방식이다.</p>\n<p>그런데 만약 3개의 서버가 있는데 하나의 서버에서 세션을 사용한 사람들만 남으면 어떻게 될까??</p>\n<p>과부하로 이어질수 있으며 만약 서버가 다운되면 세션이 사라지게되고 자기 데이터도 사라질 수가 있다.</p>\n<h2>Session Clustering</h2>\n<p>그래서 떠오르는 대안이 Session Clustering이다. 해당 저장소에 세션에 대한 정보를 저장함으로서, 요청이 어느 서버로 전달이 되든 세션 정보가 유지될 수 있도록 하는 방법이다.</p>\n<p>다만, 이렇게 될 경우 서버 외부에 세션을 저장하는 것이므로, 관리 포인트가 늘어나게 되며, 통신 과정에서 어쩔 수 없는 지연이 발생합니다. 그래서 지연이 적은 Redis와 같은 인메모리 데이터베이스가 많이 사용된다.</p>\n<h2>Session Clustering 실습하기</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>의존성 추가하기</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">implementation 'org.springframework.session:spring-session-data-redis'</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>원래 안됬던 8081 작동 되는지 확인하기</li>\n</ul>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 87.27272727272728%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/3756864674ae36d2b8377055648d6606/c9b55/2-1-tom-8081.webp 165w,\n/static/3756864674ae36d2b8377055648d6606/f2908/2-1-tom-8081.webp 330w,\n/static/3756864674ae36d2b8377055648d6606/cc661/2-1-tom-8081.webp 660w,\n/static/3756864674ae36d2b8377055648d6606/a66df/2-1-tom-8081.webp 990w,\n/static/3756864674ae36d2b8377055648d6606/d33d4/2-1-tom-8081.webp 1320w,\n/static/3756864674ae36d2b8377055648d6606/89344/2-1-tom-8081.webp 1340w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/3756864674ae36d2b8377055648d6606/04c57/2-1-tom-8081.png 165w,\n/static/3756864674ae36d2b8377055648d6606/d9ecf/2-1-tom-8081.png 330w,\n/static/3756864674ae36d2b8377055648d6606/1f083/2-1-tom-8081.png 660w,\n/static/3756864674ae36d2b8377055648d6606/7a3d6/2-1-tom-8081.png 990w,\n/static/3756864674ae36d2b8377055648d6606/78958/2-1-tom-8081.png 1320w,\n/static/3756864674ae36d2b8377055648d6606/acf8f/2-1-tom-8081.png 1340w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/3756864674ae36d2b8377055648d6606/1f083/2-1-tom-8081.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"http://localhost:8081/get\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p><a href=\"http://localhost:8081/get\">http://localhost:8081/get</a></p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<ul>\n<li>더이상 Tomcat을 사용하지 않기 때문에 JSESSIONID 대신 SESSION이라는 새로운 쿠키를 사용</li>\n<li>Redis 확인하기</li>\n</ul>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 87.27272727272728%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/effaff05bfdfba5ad8da3036da867cff/c9b55/2-1-redis-web.webp 165w,\n/static/effaff05bfdfba5ad8da3036da867cff/f2908/2-1-redis-web.webp 330w,\n/static/effaff05bfdfba5ad8da3036da867cff/cc661/2-1-redis-web.webp 660w,\n/static/effaff05bfdfba5ad8da3036da867cff/a66df/2-1-redis-web.webp 990w,\n/static/effaff05bfdfba5ad8da3036da867cff/d33d4/2-1-redis-web.webp 1320w,\n/static/effaff05bfdfba5ad8da3036da867cff/44ab2/2-1-redis-web.webp 1339w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/effaff05bfdfba5ad8da3036da867cff/04c57/2-1-redis-web.png 165w,\n/static/effaff05bfdfba5ad8da3036da867cff/d9ecf/2-1-redis-web.png 330w,\n/static/effaff05bfdfba5ad8da3036da867cff/1f083/2-1-redis-web.png 660w,\n/static/effaff05bfdfba5ad8da3036da867cff/7a3d6/2-1-redis-web.png 990w,\n/static/effaff05bfdfba5ad8da3036da867cff/78958/2-1-redis-web.png 1320w,\n/static/effaff05bfdfba5ad8da3036da867cff/cad6c/2-1-redis-web.png 1339w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/effaff05bfdfba5ad8da3036da867cff/1f083/2-1-redis-web.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"Redis\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>Redis</p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>잘 작동하는 걸 확인 할 수가 있다.</p>","categories":["ALL","Redis"],"date":"August 06, 2024","description":"Redis","id":"17ec6248-9aad-59f1-b3f7-2232349fe283","keywords":["Redis","단기 심화 부트캠프","Sparta"],"slug":"/my-first-article/redis/redis5/","title":"[Redis] HttpSession과 Session Clustering","readingTime":{"text":"6 min read"}},"listingPagePath":"/blog"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3262260831","948380417"],"slicesMap":{}}